ation facilities, as well as international gastronomy. Enjoy a relaxing holiday - whether alone, with family, partner or friends! The location is ideal because of its proximity to Ahungalla (500 m), Benota (15 km) and 130 km away from the Colombo Int’l Airport (CMB). The hotel has 501 comfortably furnished rooms and offers many modern amenities. Relax in the spa area or get in shape at the gym. 3 outdoor pools, 1 children’s pool. RiuLand Kids Club (ages 4-7 & 8-12 years) and for adults, day and evening entertainment. For lovers of gastronomy, live cooking stations at our main restaurant. Asian and Italian specialty restaurants and 4 bars and “Pacha” discotheque.Read more','/Commerce?p=TABAIndependentHotels&src=137906824&geo=10039170&from=Hotel_Review&area=&slot=1&matchID=1&oos=0&cnt=1&silo=30356&bucket=895555&nrank=1&crank=1&clt=CLD&ttype=ContactLinkDesktop&tm=241331915&managed=false&capped=false&gosox=-IsRjQQ5mD0PaCVhKGGxp2hTE6Qe5YfmqfRSR91TZESeXKZHf5phHV4nr0qfitU2NGi9I6nuBPmXmunT2F7Y2XJTbz1xAFmOM68w8YyDdXE&adults=2&child_rm_ages=&inDay=4&outDay=5&rooms=1&dated=true&inMonth=9&inYear=2022&outMonth=9&outYear=2022&def_d=true&bapid=1&cs=1ae053aee3830cdd2dc113393a208c0fd&ba_uid=536f8c41-7533-4d7f-a216-de0bc12f6734','5.0','6.309913','80.033890','https://www.tripadvisor.com//Hotel_Review-g608521-d10039170-Reviews-Hotel_Riu_Sri_Lanka-Ahungalla_Galle_District_Southern_Province.html'),(10,1852,'Galle Face Hotel','29,225','2,841','2 Galle Road, Colombo 300 Sri Lanka',NULL,'Since its beginnings in 1864 The Galle Face Hotel has been part of Colombo heritage, catering to world travellers, the property stands as one of the most storied hotels in Asia. Oozing history from every pore, timeless traditions and character abounds in each of our 156 guestrooms, restored to reflect the Galle Face Hotel’s rich past. Many rooms offer spectacular sea views, some with private balcony, and all furnished in elegant colonial style décor. Whether a sophisticated afternoon tea at The Verandah or dinner at 1864 Restaurant, a Pimms on the Chequerboard or a Cuban experience at King of the Mambo, dining experiences are a ‘must do’ whilst in Colombo. A wedding day at the Grand Ballroom or Jubilee Ballroom makes for a truly memorable and occasion. Come and experience the magic of The Galle Face Hotel on your next visit to Sri Lanka.Read more',NULL,'4.0','6.920018','79.845970','https://www.tripadvisor.com//Hotel_Review-g293962-d2038179-Reviews-Galle_Face_Hotel-Colombo_Western_Province.html'),(11,400,'Radisson Blu Resort, Galle','47,138','1,924','523C Colombo Road, Galle 80280 Sri Lanka',NULL,'Your Own Private Paradise. What makes Radisson Blu Resort, Galle your own private paradise? We’re secluded in front of a vast rain forest on Sri Lanka’s southwest coast, with every room facing the dynamic Indian Ocean. It’s your ideal vantage point to drink in the incredible Sri Lankan sunsets from your own private balcony every evening. Adding some extra sparkle to your stay, we’re close to Galle Fort, a UNESCO World Heritage Site; Unawatuna Peace Pagoda, a Buddhist shrine built by Japanese monks; and Hikkaduwa National Park, a coral sanctuary where you can view marine turtles and exotic fish.Read more',NULL,'4.5','6.052036','80.181252','https://www.tripadvisor.com//Hotel_Review-g297896-d10954536-Reviews-Radisson_Blu_Resort_Galle-Galle_Galle_District_Southern_Province.html'),(12,1852,'Shangri-La Colombo','57,908','2,036','1 Galle Face Colombo 2, Colombo 00200 Sri Lanka','0117888288','Shangri-La Hotel, Colombo offers some of the finest accommodation in the country, inclusive of 541 luxurious rooms, suites, and serviced apartments, amazing restaurants, spa and health club and the largest event space catering to up to 2,000 guests. categoriesRead more','/Commerce?p=TABAIndependentHotels&src=188443659&geo=12720953&from=Hotel_Review&area=&slot=1&matchID=1&oos=0&cnt=1&silo=30356&bucket=940655&nrank=1&crank=1&clt=CLD&ttype=ContactLinkDesktop&tm=241334036&managed=false&capped=false&